OL,3,CMan jailed after robbing Tesco at
OL,4,Cknife point and urinating on himself
OL,6,FA man who held a Tesco worker at knife
OL,7,Fpoint, urinated on himself and smeared
OL,8,Fblood on his cell walls has been
OL,9,Fjailed for seven years.
OL,11,FBradley Stacey, 21, of Stapleford Way,
OL,12,FPenhill, appeared at Swindon Crown
OL,13,FCourt on Tuesday 9 April.
OL,15,FHe had pleaded guilty to robbery,
OL,16,Fpossession of a bladed article, two
OL,17,Fcounts of criminal damage and S4A
OL,18,Fpublic order at a hearing in January.
