OL,3,CMan jailed after robbing Tesco at
OL,4,Cknife point and urinating on himself
OL,6,FOn December 8 2023, Stacey entered the
OL,7,FTesco Abbey Meads store in Swindon and
OL,8,Fheld a staff member at knife point
OL,9,Fwhile demanding money from the till.
OL,11,FThe alarm was triggered and Stacey was
OL,12,Fswiftly located nearby and arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of robbery and possession of
OL,14,Fa bladed article.
OL,16,FHe was then further arrested on
OL,17,Fsuspicion of criminal damage after
OL,18,Fspitting in the back of the police
OL,19,Fvan, before urinating on self-harm
OL,20,Fclothing he had been provided.
