OL,3,CMan jailed after robbing Tesco at
OL,4,Cknife point and urinating on himself
OL,6,FWe went on to damage the bedding in
OL,7,Fhis custody cell and smear blood on
OL,8,Fthe walls.
OL,10,FHe was also further arrested for a
OL,11,Fpublic order offence after making
OL,12,Fverbal threats towards officers.
OL,14,FDC Sally Booth of Swindon CID said:
OL,15,F"There can be no justification for
OL,16,FStacey's actions, which understandably
OL,17,Fleft the staff members present at
OL,18,FTesco feeling incredibly upset and
OL,19,Fshaken by what happened.
