OL,3,CMan jailed after robbing Tesco at
OL,4,Cknife point and urinating on himself
OL,6,F"Stacey also subjected our officers to
OL,7,Fa horrible barrage of abuse and
OL,8,Fthreats after he was arrested for the
OL,9,Frobbery, as well as requiring officers
OL,10,Fto clean up after him after his
OL,11,Factions in the police van and cell.
OL,13,F"Nobody, whether it's an officer or a
OL,14,Fmember of the public, should have to
OL,15,Fdeal with these kinds of things while
OL,16,Fgoing about their work.
OL,18,F"I'm pleased that Stacey's actions
OL,19,Fhave resulted in a lengthy jail
OL,20,Fsentence for him."
